|  5 | 王强      | NULL |
+----+-----------+------+
6 rows in set (0.00 sec)

右连接，以右的表的基准
delete from  student where id=3;
select s.id,s.name,m.mark from student as s right join mark as m  on m.stu_id=s.id order by mark;
+------+--------+------+
| id   | name   | mark |
+------+--------+------+
| NULL | NULL   |   37 |
|    2 | 小红   |   58 |
|    2 | 小红   |   61 |
